<h1>Contact</h1>

<p>
I am open to PostgreSQL architecture consulting engagements globally and 
full-time Data & Cloud Architecture roles within India.
</p>

<p>
For consulting inquiries, architecture reviews, migration advisory, or 
performance optimization discussions, please use the form below.
</p>

<form action={formAction} method="POST">
  <div>
    <label>Name</label>
    <input type="text" name="name" required />
  </div>

  <div>
    <label>Email</label>
    <input type="email" name="email" required />
  </div>

  <div>
    <label>Organization</label>
    <input type="text" name="organization" />
  </div>

  <div>
    <label>Project Details</label>
    <textarea name="message" rows="6" required></textarea>
  </div>

  <button type="submit">Send Inquiry</button>
</form>

